Name: Dreamstate Racing
About the game: Race against your friends or alone in an 'aesthetic' environment in this arcade racing game. Features up to 4-player local multiplayer 6 different cars 2 levels badly driving bots amazing music Credits: We are a small team of students who made this game as a two months learning project. Code: Tomi Sepänmaa Joonas Aro Miro Mäkinen Tapio Kemppainen Timo Rautiainen Art: Jesper Hillberg Max Männikkö Venja Vitikka
